pkgmetadata.longdescription: Exploring Election and Census Highly Informative Data Nationally for Australia // Data from the six Australian Federal Elections (House of Representatives) between 2001 and 2016, and from the four Australian Censuses over the same period. Includes tools for visualizing and analysing the data, as well as imputing Census data for years in which a Census does not occur. This package incorporates data that is copyright Commonwealth of Australia (Australian Electoral Commission) 2016.
